<br>
I must admit to not having had time really to test the new charm out so can't post any information myself.<br>
<br>
Was interested in hearing other people experiences, have you found your way around them? does the resist adjust make a difference? Have you altered you play style to compensate?<br>
<br>
Any zones that are now not possible that were before? (I have heard PoTactocs pit is quite painful now)<br>
<br>
I'll post what I find as soon as I get a chance to actually play !!<br>
<br>
